Achievements.Description: Venus cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Stop it on the frame for a few seconds where the 5th rocket explodes when touching the Terracon ship
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber

Achievements.Title: [VOID] Luckintada lei Mothee Featuro XII – Uranoo
Achievements.Description: Uranus cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Stop it on the frame for a few seconds where Xed's ship guidance system detected the target and made the appropriate sound
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber

Achievements.Title: [VOID] Luckintada lei Mothee Featuro XIII – Neptoon
Achievements.Description: Neptune cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Stop it for a few secondson the last frame where you can witness the robot vacuum cleaner
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber

Achievements.Title: [VOID] Luckintada lei Mothee Featuro XIV – Jupitarro
Achievements.Description: Jupiter cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Stop it for a few seconds on the moment where you can see an absolutely white screen
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber

Achievements.Title: [VOID] Luckintada lei Mothee Featuro XV – Terra
Achievements.Description: Bad ending cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Stop it on the last frame for a few seconds where you can witness the tail of dragonfly
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber

Achievements.Title: [VOID] Luckintada lei Mothee Featuro XVI – Woona
Achievements.Description: Final cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Just look around for some time
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber

Achievements.Title: [VOID] Luckintada lei Mothee Featuro XVII – Cortda Of Notrete
Achievements.Description: "Hall Of Fame" cutscene. Cheat mode ON. Movie controls ON. Plutese only. Stop it for a few seconds on the frame where you can see the name "Simon Pick" without crown above the face.
Achievements.Author: DimensionBomber
